title: fILEzILLA VER3.0.2.1
description:
FileZilla Features
OverviewFileZilla Client is a fast and reliable cross-platform FTP, FTPS and SFTP client with lots of useful features and an intuitive interface.

FeaturesAmong others, the features of FileZilla include the following:

Easy to use 
Supports FTP, FTP over SSL/TLS (FTPS) and SSH File Transfer Protocol (SFTP) 
Cross-platform. Runs on Windows, Linux, *BSD, OSX and more 
Available in many languages 
Supports resume and transfer of large files >4GB 
Powerful Site Manager and transfer queue 
Drag & drop support 
Configurable Speed limits

Filename filters 
Network configuration wizard
